ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this course to all students. Presenting is an extremely important skill in almost every career trajectory. This course provides concepts and examples for clear presentation styles. It is rare for students to be good presenters without lots of practice and feedback, both of which are provided in a supportive environment in this course.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Presentations are extremely important during graduate school and beyond. I have gained skills that I can apply for every presentation that I make in the future.
